source.name: Federal Logistics Information Service Program (FLIS) Enterprise Business System (EBS) Query
source.description: The Federal Logistics Information Service Program (FLIS) Enterprise Business System (EBS) is a web-based public inquiry tool designed to query EBS items of supply with certain Reference Number Category Codes (RNCC) and Reference Number Variation Codes (RVCC) combined.  WebFlis EBS tool queries by National Stock Number (NSN) or National Identification Number (NIIN), or Part Number (PN).
